  "Subtitle": {
    "English": "Personal Reality Flux Monitor",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "个体现实波动监测仪",
    "TraditionalChinese": "個人現實通量顯示器"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "Nada has detected a new pattern emerging in the stories of the <TRANS_TRA>Gek<>, <TRANS_EXP>Korvax<>, and <TRANS_WAR>Vy'keen<>.<br><br>The dosimeter measures exposure to <span class=\"name name-special\">historiographical flux</span> around key artifact sites. Recordings of unusual historical shifts will enable Nada to trace the signal.<br><br>Assist Nada and Polo in their research by using this device to <span class=\"name name-stellar\">transmit historial data</span> from alien artifact sites.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "纳达从<TRANS_TRA>吉克<>、<TRANS_EXP>科尔瓦克斯<>和<TRANS_WAR>维吉恩<>的故事中找到了一种新的模式。<br><br>剂量仪能够测量关键遗物地点周围<span class=\"name name-special\">史学波动</span>的暴露情况。记录不寻常的历史转变将使纳达能够追踪信号。<br><br>在研究中协助纳达和保罗，使用该设备从外星遗物地点<span class=\"name name-stellar\">传输历史数据</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "納達在<TRANS_TRA>吉客族<>、<TRANS_EXP>科瓦族<>和<TRANS_WAR>維金族<>的故事中偵測到有新的模式浮現。<br><br>劑量計裝置會測量關鍵器物地點周圍的<span class=\"name name-special\">史學史通量</span>暴露度。透過不尋常的歷史偏移紀錄，納達得以追蹤信號。<br><br>使用這個裝置從外星器物地點<span class=\"name name-stellar\">傳輸歷史資料</span>，協助納達與波羅的研究。"
  },
